    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Lathes having a mandrel, which is a shaft or spindle to which work is fixed while being turned in the lathe.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
